          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1630487693539-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Add 3/4<strong> </strong>of the <strong>ayam betutu paste</strong> to the chicken and give everything a good mix up until it's fully coated in the paste</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) and golden – this is your<strong> Balinese-style ayam betutu chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1630487704984-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
