        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has been in the oven for 20 min, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> remaining ayam betutu paste </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 6,
