    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>mangetout</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Wash, then add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further or until wilted – these are your <strong>spiced greens</strong></p>",
