      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Balinese-style ayam betutu chicken</strong> with the <strong>spiced greens </strong>and<strong> cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining roasted peanuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
